metadata.name: Aphrodite's Gaze
metadata.description:
With radiant grace, Aphrodite gazes tenderly upon her adoring lovers, casting her celestial gaze from the heavens above. 

Her ethereal beauty illuminates the sky, a captivating sight that captures hearts and kindles passion in those fortunate enough to be touched by her divine presence.

Digital Painting by Idil Yozer.
2023.
